## Fragment Caching in Views

### Basic Fragment Cache

```erb
<!-- Cache entire sidebar -->
<% cache 'sidebar', expires_in: 1.hour do %>
  <aside class="w-64 bg-gray-50 p-4">
    <h3 class="font-bold mb-4">Categories</h3>
    <ul>
      <% Category.all.each do |category| %>
        <li><%= link_to category.name, category %></li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
  </aside>
<% end %>
```

### Cache with Model Dependency

```erb
<!-- Cache invalidates when article is updated -->
<% cache @article do %>
  <article class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4"><%= @article.title %></h1>
    <div class="prose">
      <%= @article.body %>
    </div>
  </article>
<% end %>
```

### Cache with Multiple Dependencies

```erb
<!-- Cache key includes article and user -->
<% cache ['article-card', @article, Current.user] do %>
  <div class="card">
    <h2><%= @article.title %></h2>
    
    <!-- Show edit button only to author -->
    <% if @article.user == Current.user %>
      <%= link_to "Edit", edit_article_path(@article) %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
<% end %>
```

### Cache with Version

```erb
<!-- Add version to bust cache when layout changes -->
<% cache ['article-card', @article, 'v2'] do %>
  <div class="new-card-layout">
    <%= render @article %>
  </div>
<% end %>
```

